## clippy - Install Clippy, Rust Code Linter
## nightly - Enable Nightly Features
## rust-analyzer - Install Rust Analyzer, a Rust compiler front-end for IDEs
## rust-fmt - Install rustfmt, Rust code formatter
## rust-src - Install rust-src, needed by developer tools and for build-std (cross)
dev-lang/rust-bin clippy rust-analyzer rustfmt rust-src
